///rdd/////////////
collection java objects that follow immutablity, fault tolerance , laziness  properties called RDD
2 ways to create rdd ... 1) parallalise 2) textFile("path")

if a scala function/method feel lazy to process ..... transformations: map, filter,
a scala function/method doesn't feel lazy to process called ... action: collect,take


